            <title>[HBASE-1077] Master does not reassign regions closed while opening</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1077</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a regionserver encounters an error &amp;#8211; for example a transient DFS problem &amp;#8211; while opening a region, it will send a CLOSE to the master. The master never tries reassigning the region after this, as if the CLOSE is ignored. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
